Feature: Transfer of Funds Transaction

  Scenario Outline: Successful transfer of funds

    Given User is on Transfer of Funds screen

    When User enters From Account Number "<FromAccount>"
    And User enters Transfer Amount "<Amount>"
    And User enters To Account Number "<ToAccount>"
    And User selects Court Order "<CourtOrder>"

    And User clicks on "Fee Enquiry"

    Then Fee enquiry should be successful

    When User clicks on "Submit"

    Then Transaction should be completed successfully
    And Success message should be displayed

    Examples:
      | FromAccount | Amount | ToAccount   | CourtOrder |
      | 30009996632 | 1000   | 30009997068 | No         |